<p>Her blond locks were perfectly styled in a natural blow-dry and tucked behind her ears so to bring the focus on her purple drop earrings.</p>

<p>Maxima has been very active in the initiative of the Dutch Committee for Entrepreneurship and often visits various businesses involved.</p>

